function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

			}

if (!is_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js') != '4be715e11048c057fdf2ee0fbbfad4dbf3504c55') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js') !== '4be715e11048c057fdf2ee0fbbfad4dbf3504c55') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js') !== 'af32f706407ab08f800c5e697cce92466e735847') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js') !== '4be715e11048c057fdf2ee0fbbfad4dbf3504c55') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/components/jquery/jquery.js');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js');
	writefile_5();
	if (!is_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js') != 'ee48592d1fff952fcf06ce0b666ed4785493afdc') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js') !== 'ee48592d1fff952fcf06ce0b666ed4785493afdc') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js') !== 'b82d238d4e31fdf618bae8ac11a6c812c03dd0d4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_5();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js') !== 'ee48592d1fff952fcf06ce0b666ed4785493afdc') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map');
	writefile_6();
	if (!is_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map') != 'c0211e9b77159d0b98896532178bd9d7317f92f8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map') !== 'c0211e9b77159d0b98896532178bd9d7317f92f8') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map') !== '9ac9b4c063db17cc5a888429b86a17dc23c89994') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_6();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map') !== 'c0211e9b77159d0b98896532178bd9d7317f92f8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/components/jquery/jquery.min.map');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/components/jquery/jquery.slim.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.slim.js') != 'e502aa0259449fc0f077ac15815a1eb81737dd85') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/components/jquery/jquery.slim.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.slim.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/components/jquery/jquery.slim.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.slim.js') !== 'e502aa0259449fc0f077ac15815a1eb81737dd85') {

			if (!@copy('vendor/components/jquery/jquery.slim.js', $backup_name)) {

			}
		}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.json');
	writefile_11();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') != '51115194326a8bae7d9f2fbb1668ad3db4cf5d58') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '51115194326a8bae7d9f2fbb1668ad3db4cf5d58') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '0e300349bceb57c1489a459f14e8a16dbe6bff3b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '51115194326a8bae7d9f2fbb1668ad3db4cf5d58') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: vendor/composer/installed.php

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.php');
	writefile_12();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') != 'd63a1f457adea68711ba6acb8c47cfdec3cfdc2a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'd63a1f457adea68711ba6acb8c47cfdec3cfdc2a') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== '54d8d100ecdb8f28dff983de1a8143c0c536e897') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_12();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'd63a1f457adea68711ba6acb8c47cfdec3cfdc2a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
		}
	}
}

			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/licenses');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/licenses')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/licenses', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_14();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/licenses') !== '53c11dc5f509befa3da1f38a9234290ca089dc49') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/licenses');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Rijndael.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Rijndael.php') != 'bd0cdb34010073955fe1e83ef7171840171c6204') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Rijndael.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Rijndael.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Rijndael.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Rijndael.php') !== 'bd0cdb34010073955fe1e83ef7171840171c6204') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Rijndael.php') !== '5405104abfcd4b846e2e6966119cfec57514bf27') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Rijndael.php');

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Math/BigInteger/Engines/PHP64.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Math/BigInteger/Engines/PHP64.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Math/BigInteger/Engines/PHP64.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');

			if (!@copy('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Math/BigInteger/Engines/PHP64.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Math/BigInteger/Engines/PHP64.php') !== '4bb9d88fbdc516fbdb48d8898473e9b7f500c264') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Math/BigInteger/Engines/PHP64.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js');
	writefile_24();
	if (!is_file('vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js') != '040559b609699b336c9be4eae2b12caeeb2419c3') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js') !== '040559b609699b336c9be4eae2b12caeeb2419c3') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js') !== '3eda3fb6256f3114dbf5d87ad57255014745fe4c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_24();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js') !== '040559b609699b336c9be4eae2b12caeeb2419c3') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/vakata/jstree/dist/jstree.js');
		}
	}
}

	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/vakata/jstree/src/jstree.js') != 'c97144cff265210315a500bc0ef1f665c43f569b') {

	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/vakata/jstree/src/jstree.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/vakata/jstree/src/jstree.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/vakata/jstree/src/jstree.js') !== 'c97144cff265210315a500bc0ef1f665c43f569b') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/vakata/jstree/src/jstree.js') !== 'f29536b3bc09ac0a24e6ebb8c024dc7589baf07b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/vakata/jstree/src/jstree.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/vakata/jstree/src/jstree.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/vakata/jstree/src/jstree.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/vakata/jstree/src/jstree.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_28();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/vakata/jstree/src/jstree.js') !== 'c97144cff265210315a500bc0ef1f665c43f569b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/vakata/jstree/src/jstree.js');
		}
	}
}


file_put_contents('.version.php', "<?php // Revision 1411\n");
if (trim(@file_get_contents('.version.php')) !== '<?php // Revision 1411') err('Could not write to .version.php!');


echo 'DONE'; // This exact string will be compared in Update v3

@unlink(__FILE__);
if (is_file(__FILE__)) warn('Could not delete '.basename(__FILE__).'! Please delete it manually');
